## Deploy

```bash
make install
make unit
databricks bundle deploy -t dev
databricks bundle run a2a_agent_app -t dev
```

## Configure

Edit `app.yaml` env vars or set them in the Databricks Apps Settings UI:

- `A2A_LLM_ENDPOINT={{.llm_endpoint}}`
- `A2A_AUTH_MODE={{.auth_mode}}`
- `A2A_CATALOG={{.catalog_name}}`
- `A2A_SCHEMA={{.schema_name}}`

## Customize

The file you'll edit most is `src/app/agent.py`. See the dev kit's full docs:
